// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
//  stm32wle5_devkit.repl  —  SWM Gagan / Talab on STM32WLE5JC
//
//  Platform: STM32WLE5JC (Cortex-M4F, integrated Sub-GHz radio)
//  Role:     Endpoint — Gagan OHT or Talab SPT, selected by Cargo
//            feature flag in ports/stm32wle5/.
//  Power:    Single-cell Li-ion + solar panel (MCP73831 charger).
//  Radio:    Integrated SUBGHZSPI transceiver — Phase 2 attaches the
//            LR1121-compatible model here.
//
//  Inherits the STM32WLE5 SoC; node-specific peripherals (sensor
//  stubs, battery ADC) attach below.  Layout mirrors gagan.repl.
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

using "../../../soc/arm/stm32wle5/stm32wle5.repl"

// ── Ultrasonic Level Sensor (HC-SR04-class)
// PA8=USON_PWR_EN, PA9=USON_TRIG, PA10=USON_ECHO  (SCH_SWM §3)
// Phase 2 attaches ultrasonic_stm32.py here.

// ── Battery + solar telemetry (ADC channels 0, 5)
// BAT_SENSE on PA0 (ADC_IN5), SOLAR_SENSE on PC0, CHG_STAT_N on PB15.
// The SoC's `adc` block at 0x50040000 carries both readings.

// ── Pressure sensor (I²C, BMP388/DPS310-class)
// Hooked to I²C1 (PB6/PB7).  Phase 2 attaches pressure_i2c_stm32.py.

// ── External NOR (MX25R6435F) for OTA staging
// Wired to SPI1.  Phase 2 attaches a flash model.

// ── LoRa radio (SUBGHZSPI @ 0x58010000)
// Inherited from stm32wle5.repl as a generic SPI block.
// stm32wle5_devkit.resc unregisters this and loads
// `SPI.LR1121SubGhzRadio` (byte-stream STM32 SPI variant) in its place.
